&lt;p&gt;An opportunity has arisen for a motivated Paediatric Nurse to join the Royal Free Hospital Paediatric Nursing Team. The post holder will work as part of a Team with support from the Band 6’s, Practice Education Facilitators, Ward Sister and Paediatric Matron. &lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;We are a busy general and surgical ward. We deliver high quality and World Class care to Children and young people with acute and chronic health needs, from age 0-18yrs. Our specialism includes General medicine, ENT, Gastroenterology, Plastic and General surgery. &lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Paediatric Matron, Ade Adamolekun - aadamolekun@nhs.net &lt;br /&gt;Or Ward Sister, Devleta Begic on the Ward Telephone number: 0207 830 2732.&lt;/p&gt;
